---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
		<style>
			main {
				width: 100%;
				max-width: 960px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 3em 1em;
			}
			h1 {
				font-size: 2.5rem;
				font-weight: 700;
				margin-bottom: 0.5em;
			}
			.intro {
				font-size: 1.2rem;
				line-height: 1.6;
				color: #4a5568;
				margin-bottom: 2em;
			}
			.section-title {
				font-size: 1.5rem;
				font-weight: 600;
				margin-top: 2em;
				margin-bottom: 0.75em;
				border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
				padding-bottom: 0.25em;
			}
			ul {
				list-style-type: none;
				padding: 0;
			}
			li {
				margin-bottom: 1em;
				line-height: 1.5;
			}
			.tagline {
				font-style: italic;
				color: #718096;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>Welcome to My Blog</h1>
			<p class="intro">
				I am an Electrical and Computer Engineering student exploring the intersections of hardware, 
				deep technical optimization, and systemic analysis. This space serves as an open ledger for my research, 
				engineering projects, and analytical breakdowns of complex systems.
			</p>

			<h2 class="section-title">Core Engineering & Science Focus</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>
					<strong>Thermal Dynamics & Semiconductors:</strong> Exploring solid-state cooling architectures, 
					nanoscale breakthroughs, and device-level micro-modeling.
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Embedded Systems & AI Pipelines:</strong> Engineering hardware integrations, 
					neural network optimization, and high-fidelity signal workflows.
				</li>
			</ul>

			<h2 class="section-title">Analytical Tangents & Systems</h2>
			<p>
				Beyond core engineering, I look at the world through a lens of dense calculation and structural frameworks. Expect deep dives into:
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li>
					<strong>Positional Chess Theory:</strong> Deconstructing concrete opening repertoires and positional calculation models for the competitive player.
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Tennis Dynamics:</strong> Analyzing technical execution, biometric efficiencies, and the mathematical optimization of elite performance.
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Global Economics & Geopolitics:</strong> Mapping out macroeconomic trends, trade networks, and the geopolitical forces shaping the global technology and semiconductor landscape.
				</li>
			</ul>

			<h2 class="section-title">Recent Updates</h2>
			<p>
				Head over to the <a href="/blog">Blog</a> tab to explore published entries, ranging from rigorous tactical chess matrices to thermodynamic deep dives.
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>